You are someone who is more focused on tasks, goals, and results when facing challenges, obstacles, and the environment. You tend to have a firm, confident, and results-oriented personality. You have the courage to take risks, make quick decisions, and do not hesitate to influence others to achieve what you want. However, this trait can also make you appear impatient, too direct, or critical of people you consider slow or less competent. Your success is measured by achieving goals efficiently, and you are often motivated by power, control, or the drive to overcome big challenges.
Someone who can balance their dominant traits, like the Steadiness (S) type
